            "tldr": "MFS HR 0.53 and OS HR 0.60 adding 2yr abiraterone to ADT+RT in high-risk M0 prostate.",
            "details": [
              "📊 Combination (abi±enza) vs ADT control — comparison values omitted (cell value \"0.53\" not verified in source)",
              "📊 6-yr MFS 82% (79-85) combination vs 69% (66-72) control",
              "📊 Adding enzalutamide to abiraterone gave no extra MFS benefit: interaction HR 1.02 (0.70-1.50), p=0.91",
              "🔍 Meta-analysis pooling 2 randomised phase 3 STAMPEDE trials, N=1974, open-label, 113 UK/Swiss sites, median f/u 72mo",
              "🔍 RT mandated for N0, encouraged for N+; 74Gy/37fx to prostate+SV or hypofrac equivalent; 85% planned RT",
              "💊 Abiraterone 1000mg + prednisolone 5mg daily × 2yr on a 3yr ADT backbone",
              "🔍 39% node-positive; median PSA 34ng/mL; median age 68 (IQR 63-73)",
              "🔗 Extends abiraterone benefit from metastatic HSPC (LATITUDE, STAMPEDE M1) into the high-risk M0 curative setting"
